ogTitle: OneKey® MLS Selects MLS Grid as Solution to Data Feed Management
twitter:description: OneKey® MLS joins a growing list of multiple listing services which rely on MLS Grid to manage data feed licensing and delivery. MLS Grid works with more than 1,455 data consumers and supports more than 70,000 data licenses nationwide, and represents more the 360,000 MLS subscribers.
